data.description: Experience urban luxury living at its finest at Cornerstone Village, a premier loft-style condo building nestled in the heart of Midtown Atlanta, between 5th & 6th streets and Peachtree Street. This top-floor end unit floods with ample natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere with stunning skyline views that include the historic Biltmore Hotel. Enjoy the modern and new stainless-steel appliances, fresh interior paint, and updated flooring - making this unit feel brand new! This exclusive property offers a host of amenities including secure covered garage parking, concierge services, a fitness center, pool, and an array of community features such as a clubroom, conference room, dog run, outdoor kitchen, and theater room. It gets better, step outside your door to find yourself just a short stroll away from the iconic Fox Theatre, renowned for its cultural significance and world-class performances. Nearby, Piedmont Park, Georgia Tech, CVS, Publix, MARTA, and a diverse selection of dining, shopping, and entertainment options await, providing unparalleled access to everything Midtown has to offer. With GA State University, Emory University Hospital Midtown, and major highways in proximity, everything you need is within reach. Move-in ready to enjoy, this condo offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. Make sure you seize this opportunity to experience this top-tier location without the top-tier price tag. Contact us now to schedule your exclusive viewing and make Cornerstone Village your new home!
